data.description: Don't miss this 4 bedroom, 2 full bath, 1768 square foot 1/2 Duplex!  The owner has put a lot of updates into the home to include: new flooring, fresh paint, updated lighting, new back patio, foundation restoration, drain system, 3 new sump pumps, new escape window in southwest bedroom, new french doors, and so much more. The home sits in a quiet neighborhood with serene nature setting just across the street. Take a look today!  New window well cover is on order and should arrive in February. With acceptable offer, seller agrees to have yard seeded in spring.
